# Decision Tracking Rules

## Recording Decisions
- Document in decisions.md
- Include date and context
- State rationale
- List alternatives considered
- Note impact on implementation

## Decision Format
- Clear statement of decision
- Background and context
- Analysis of options
- Chosen solution
- Implementation impact

## Security Decisions
- Document in security.md
- Include risk assessment
- Note mitigation strategies
- Update security documentation
- Track implementation

## Architecture Decisions
- Update architecture.md
- Include diagrams if needed
- Document interfaces
- Note compatibility impacts
- Update tooling if needed 